==English==
===Adjective===
'''nang''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''nanger''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''nangest''')

# (''slang'') Very good. Cool.
#: ''This new dubplate is totally nang!''

===Noun===
'''nang''' (''[[plural]]'' '''nangs''')

# (''slang'') A metal bulb filled with [[Nitrous Oxide Gas]], intended as a propellent for whipped cream. This gas is often inhaled for its disassociative effects, and the term nang is common drug slang in [[Australia]].
#: ''Have a nang''

